- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper discusses information transmission over fiber optic channels using a generalized Nonlinear Fourier Transform. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper develops numerical algorithms to compute the direct and inverse GNFTs. 
- cs.SI (Systems and Control): The paper deals with communication systems and their robustness to practical impairments. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses algorithms for computing the GNFT. 
- cs.SP (Signal Processing): The paper deals with signal processing in the context of fiber optic communication.
